You are a code reviewer performing Round 2 re-review after fixes for Batch 3 (Task 8).

## Round 1 Findings (FAIL)
- F001 (HIGH, code-bug): Concurrent batches shared AsyncSession unsafely.
  FIX: execute() now checks ctx.db; when not None, falls back to serial even for concurrent batches.
- F002 (HIGH, code-bug): run_one() bypassed registry dual-signature, legacy tools crashed.
