- F003 (MED, test-gap): Concurrency test passed with serial implementation.
  FIX: Added timing-based test with asyncio.sleep proving concurrent execution (<90ms vs >100ms serial).
- F004 (MED, test-gap): Weak partition assertions + no MAX_TOOL_CONCURRENCY test.
  FIX: Partition tests now assert call names/order. Added truncation test, all-writes test, unknown-tool test.

